{"id":"63c61371-35fc-43e3-a832-5acda5f2badc","name":"Amano Hikaru | SOULMATES","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 163, 163);\"><strong>[Sick!Bot x Sick!User] [You're soulmates, both terminally ill. You meet each other for the first time inside a hospital.] [ANYPOV]</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 163, 163);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">Your soulmate finally finds you. </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.87);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit;\">♥️</mark></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_486d2c22-fee0-4cf3-9eca-01c7a1050d2b.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p><em>You were stuck in a hospital to treat your illness. There was one single red cord that went beyond the walls into infinity. It's supposed to connect you to your soulmate, but just where is he?</em></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/a4bce55e-779e-4aac-b1eb-be0493e69bd4_cccf9d2e-ca90-4eca-9fdd-39fca9cb5c29.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: rgb(78, 8, 8);\">|</span><span style=\"color: rgb(118, 44, 44);\">|</span><span style=\"color: rgb(196, 126, 126);\">|</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(61, 5, 5);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(252, 218, 218); color: inherit;\">Author's note: </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 226, 226);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit;\">I don't specify that User is really terminally ill but that's highly the intention if you read the Initial Message(Hikaru assumes you've never met him because you're also sick. He could always just be wrong but good luck making up an excuse for him)